          "reviewBody": "Not the right place to put your child.. its a sham.. my child has not been provided any opportunity to grow in scopes and arts. There are issues with favoritism.. all activities are name sake.. everything Is about money making. Bus facilities also su ks.. there are better schools in Greatet noida. Please try there.\nNot recommend.",
