          },
          "datePublished": "2022-04-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The most casual approach of the school i have ever experienced or heard about, i have done admission of my son for pre nursery, and from very first day the mis management of the school got floated, they have directed parents to send the school with name stapled on uniform (as if we are sending the couriers with name tagged and someone will receive them at school) They have provided the bus route post many follow ups with all incomplete details,and with the driver number to talk while he might be driving, i have not sent my kid form two days and no one called me for the assurance that he came to school or not. Response time is very poor, i have decided to cancel the admission and will send my kid to a school where the priority is of the safety and professionalism. The school bus got delayed by 20 mins in second day,  I urge others to please do not decide just on the name of the school. I have experienced the worst from them. The reason they are giving that it is first day of school so this happened. ( KR mangalam Greater Noida)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
