          },
          "reviewBody": "K R Manglam chain of school is getting popularity due to good facility plus faculty members, presently KR Manglam school are at GK-1; Gurgoan; Greater Noida; Vaishali; Vikashpuri. KR Manglam University at Sohna Road is also offerings different courses. For the last 15 years this chain of school getting popularity amongst students.",
          "publisher": {
